premise_source_doc_sentence: From 1969 to 2011 , the history of Libya was marked by the Libyan Arab Jamahiriya  (  where jamahiriya means `` state of the masses ''  )  , a `` direct democracy '' political system established by Muammar Gaddafi , who nominally stepped down from power in 1977 , but remained an unofficial `` Brother Leader '' until 2011 .
